パッケージ manhattan.waveformdata

  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    BasicID
    ID for observed and synthetic waveform This class is IMMUTABLE
    Double values will be rounded off to 3rd decimal places.
    BasicIDFile
    Utilities for a pair of an ID file and a waveform file.
    PartialID
    ID for a partial derivative This class is IMMUTABLE
    type: String(s), Float(f), Integer(i), Long(l), Boolean(b)
    =Contents of information for one ID=
    Name of station (must be 8 or less letters) 8Byte(s)
    Name of network (must be 8 or less letters) 8Byte(s)
    Horizontal position of station (latitude longitude) 4Byte*2(f*2)
    Global CMT ID 15Byte(s)
    Component (ZRT) 1Byte
    Period minimum and maximum 4Byte*2(f*2)
    Start time 4Byte(f)
    Number of points 4Byte(i)
    Sampling Hz 4Byte(f)
    If one is convoluted or observed, true 1Byte(b)
    Position of a waveform for the ID 8Byte(l)
    partial type 1Byte
    Location of a perturbation point: latitude, longitude, radius 4Byte*3(f*3) One ID volume:PartialID.oneIDbyte: 82
    PartialIDFile
    Utilities for a pair of an ID file and a waveform file.
    WaveformDataWriter
    BasicDatasetやPartialDatasetの書き込み This class will not overwrite.
